Avalara
” or “
us
” or “
our
”) and Customer. If a provision of this Avalara Europe Ltd. Services Data Processing Agreement (“
DPA
”) conflicts with a provision of the Contract, the provision in this DPA governs. Capitalised terms used and not otherwise defined in this DPA have the meanings provided in the Contract.
