LIST OF SUB-PROCESSORS
MODULE TWO: Transfer controller to processor
MODULE THREE: Transfer processor to processor
The controller has provided general authorisation for the engagement of subprocessors from an agreed list, available at
Subprocessors (avalara.com)
.
