Visa Privacy Center
Visa values your trust and respects your privacy. This Privacy Center will help you understand how we collect, use, and share your Personal Information. You can also find links to help you exercise your privacy rights.
Global Privacy Notice
Our
Global Privacy Notice
explains how we collect, use and disclose Personal Information.
We also have a
Cookie Notice
that explains our practices with regard to cookies, tags and similar types of online data that we collect.
