Analytics
Description
This cookie has a value pair of guid = randomly generated string of characters and numbers. Used for data lookup which allows the dynamic pulling of data from the Eloqua system for use on a given web page. The range of data that can be returned is virtually unlimited allowing for Contact, Prospect, Data Card, Group membership or Visitor data to be returned. Data lookups are used to populate data in a form or validate if the contact is part of an email group.
